# Dependencies / build output (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/out

# Local env & secrets — never bake into images
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.*.example

# VCS / editor / OS noise
.git
.gitignore
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log

# Docs & infra that don't affect the build
docs
**/*.md
!README.md

# Foundry / contracts artifacts
contracts/**/out
contracts/**/cache
contracts/**/broadcast
